...

372
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:41,520
...

373
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:46,040
Musang botak akan ditertawakan.

374
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:49,000
Tetapi mata saya tidak dapat melihat,

375
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:53,120
